Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you miraculous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, please enjoy a different kind \Nof ending featuring mother and son!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:26.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Japan's foremost luxury train,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Royal Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I quite like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wanted to reserve the \Nwhole train for you, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I wanted to come in \Ncontact with the Japanese people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if even just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to \Nmeet that famous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:53.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What?! You contact Superintendent \NChaki directly yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean Inspector Nakamori, \Nwho is in charge of your security?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm busy! Get it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tell Superintendent Chaki that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean the visitor I had \Nin my private room earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bandit known as Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.27,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Crystal Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Your Majesty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He appeared to steal the treasure \Nof the Principality of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Europe's biggest topaz,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,this Crystal Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the advance notice sent \Nto the embassy was genuine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why didn't he take off\N with that jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he realized it at the first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That this is only a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A replica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've got the real one\N hidden elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell you that, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He could be listening in from \Nsomewhere on this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Kid is on this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:54.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Check every passenger from head to toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot subject everyone else to \Ntrouble for the sake of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:08.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a showdown between him and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This train will reach Osaka \Nin two and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be able to steal the jewel,\N as stated in his notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will I be able to protect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a duel with the honor \Nof my country on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your necklace is a little strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:29.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've instructed you countless times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Address me as "Your Majesty" \Nin front of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Phillip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of Queen Selizabeth and King Henry, \Nwho passed away from illness two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the next king of the \NPrincipality of Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...this replica is different \Nfrom the last time I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a listening device!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid must have planted it in \NHer Majesty's room when he slipped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:22.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm around, you won't \Nlay a finger on that jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:29.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you certainly have sharp eyes, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a weird expression on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That third-rate inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your old man just reamed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who wanted to \Nride this train, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked my dad\N to get us tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know. I'm always \Ngrateful to your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! You need an attitude adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And do it before we meet Her Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're on the \Nsame train as a queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we lucky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll pay her our respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce myself as the daughter of \NInspector Nakamori, who always stymies Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid has ignored our warning again \Nand is targeting another Big Jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to his advance notice, \Nthere are even more security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the circumstances, I believe it'll \Nbe tough getting the gem before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, just steal it from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever you do, be careful \Nhow you handle that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it may contain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:07:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the stone of life, Pandora, \Nwhich can grant immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now will you tell me where \Nyou're keeping the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing the location, I don't \Nknow where to focus security efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that worried about it, \Nthen stay by my side and protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pour you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No thank you, I can't \Ndrink while on duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. This is the first time anyone's \Nturned down a drink from me, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, in that case, \NI'll indulge in just one drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,European liquor is tops, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:14.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's drinking booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, this is my daughter, \NAoko, and her classmate, Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Charming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a pleasure to meet you, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doin' over here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:38.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito said he really wanted \Nto meet Her Majesty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}you{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't innerfere with security \Nby wandering aroun'! {sic}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he supposed to be protecting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, I've managed to infiltrate \NHer Majesty's salon car,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so now I can search \Nfor the jewel all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But where the heck could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:09.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just in Her Majesty's room a little \Nwhile ago, so I doubt she left it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe it's near her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In her bag or under her hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's in that cat's eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been gazing at Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I was looking at the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Majesty's cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:38.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, isn't he? He'll be two this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phillip Maximilian du Ingram!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the prince?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Caesar. \NYou wanted to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's not really possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cute teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a present from my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? One eye is about to fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:36.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't feel like it's in here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kid the Phantom Thief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't even joke about \Nsomething like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, I'm wrong? Too bad, since \NI know where the jewel is hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not gonna tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Phillip, it's dangerous \Nfor you to be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. You heard the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:29.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna help Mother \Nprotect the jewel from Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're doing it out of \Nlove for your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I hate Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She changed after Father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but now, she gets angry and yells\N every time she sees me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She says I never listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she doesn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I made Father a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to protect \Nthe country with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "Mother"! You call me "Your Majesty"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better not see you \Nout of this room again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have to be so harsh with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way to \Nget through to that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:51.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be arriving in Osaka in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've won, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So where is the jewel hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you when we reach Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll be surprised, \Nthough, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? Where the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! If I don't hurry, \NI'll miss my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:49.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, the form changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it! I know where the jewel is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be Kid the Phantom Thief\N in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally showin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just tryin' to protect Her Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, Inspector. Where's your glass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My glass is over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is your glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:09.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start looking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:21.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean the jewel was \Nin my glass with the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some audacity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal Mother is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to see you again, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a train. There's \Nnowhere for you to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, please remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief \Nis an elusive rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:17.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you're a mother \Nwith a heart before you're a queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:31.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get on the phone and have the \Npolice set up a cordon around the whole area!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:34.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:39.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you've still got the \Nbooze in your brain, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be fooled by that dummy... \NHow gullible can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's gullible, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in my country need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am impressed you managed \Nto climb up here by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A man helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you were sure to be here\N and carried me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the nice man standing \Nright behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't have \Ntime to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the jewel down and turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you want me to blow \N{\i1}this{\i0} kid's brains out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Pandora jewel you \Nand your pals are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I held it up to the moon a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm gonna check it out myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the line for the \Nimmortal Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.09,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Negishita Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:53.36,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Negishita Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:10.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:16.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the attitude you take \Nwith the guy who saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that jewel, \Nthe people in my country will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:23.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! I'm not giving \Nit back to any liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really doing it for \Nyour mother's sake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna return the jewel in \Nthe hope that she'll praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, am I on the mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've got a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:49.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to confirm your mother's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this is happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:58.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My country's precious treasure \Nwas stolen because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the people say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phillip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I chased Kid the Phantom Thief onto the \Nroof and tried to take back the jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he got it away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you ever listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always pull \Ndangerous stunts like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:47.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With your father gone, why did I harden my \Nheart and try to give you a strict upbringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is the genuine Queen of Hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, a boy mustn't bawl his eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And as I keep telling you, \Nrefer to me as "Your Highness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:48.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic trick that unlocked \NHer Majesty the Queen's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But tonight, I was \Nno more than the assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The star was a brave little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:34.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakamori with the Metro Police! \NAnd I'm in charge of this preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So as for next week's plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:41.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a Detective Delon from Europe goes over \Nmy head and claims he's gonna arrest Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:45.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this means I've gotta go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:50.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NThe Princess and the Thief's Improv.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:50.49,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess and the Thief's Improv
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:58.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, don't miss my exploits!
